headline: Gartner to Report Fourth Quarter 2025 Financial Results on February 3, 2026
summary: STAMFORD, Conn., January 20, 2026--Gartner, Inc. (NYSE: IT) will report its financial results for fourth quarter 2025 before the market opens on Tuesday, February 3, 2026. The press release and earnings supplement, with accompanying financial information, will be posted on the Gartner investor website at https://investor.gartner.com.
